00:02:32.427 --> 00:02:33.585
So, in this talk,

00:02:33.609 --> 00:02:37.511
you're going to learn
three new ways to be civil, I hope,

00:02:37.535 --> 00:02:41.863
and it will be according
to the original definition of civility.

00:02:42.394 --> 00:02:44.350
My first problem is:

00:02:45.403 --> 00:02:47.336
civility is an obsolete word.

00:02:47.684 --> 00:02:49.763
My second problem is:

00:02:49.787 --> 00:02:52.192
civility has become
a dirty word in this country.

00:02:52.708 --> 00:02:55.834
